<h1>Works of Art in Stained Glass</h1>
<p>Great Oak Glass is a stained glass and design studio based in Mid Wales, working to commission internationally. Producing individually designed glass work, very unusual <a href="/wood-carving/">hand-carved Welsh Oak fire surrounds</a> and <a href="/curved-leaded-lights/">3-D leaded lights</a>, Great Oak Glass creations speak of originality and quality.</p>
<p>We specialise in unique designs, tailored to clients' specifications, incorporating applied techniques of sandblasting, kiln-fired enamelling and etching to provide art work which augments any architectural setting. Any interior, from churches and public buildings to private residences can be enhanced by a Great Oak Glass art piece.</p><div class="testimonial"><blockquote>We were anticipating craftsmanship and inspiration of a very high order. We have not been disappointed.<br /><span><a href="/testimonials/2/">[read full testimonial]</a></span></blockquote><p class="client">Philip and Gloria Pilkington</p></div>
